# Footer


```jsx
import Footer from '@agct/react-common/src/components/Footer/Footer';

const FooterExample = () => (
  <Footer>
    <span>content</span>
  </Footer>
);
```


### Properties

| Name      | Type  | Required | Default  | Description                 |
|:----------|:------|:---------|:---------|:----------------------------|
| children  | `any` |          |          | Child elements to render    |
